query_result.query:
SELECT 
COUNT("texts"."id") * (CASE WHEN "tags"."tag_type" = 'مثبت' THEN 1
    WHEN "tags"."tag_type" = 'منفی'  THEN  -1
            ELSE 0
       END) AS "تعداد کل", DATE_TRUNC('Day',"texts"."date") AS "تاریخ", "tags"."tag_type" as "احساس", "tags"."text" as "عنوان"
FROM "public"."texts" AS "texts"
Inner Join "public"."text_tags" AS "text_tags" ON "text_tags"."text_id" = "texts"."id"
Inner Join "public"."tags" AS "tags" ON "tags"."id" = "text_tags"."tag_id"
GROUP BY "تاریخ", "احساس", "عنوان"
ORDER BY "تاریخ" desc, "tags"."tag_type" desc
